    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) that defines mechanical excellence. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering a linear power band through six individual throttle bodies and high-pressure dual-VANOS variable valve timing. The 6-speed Getrag manual transmission offers tactile gear engagement, complemented by a factory-spec variable M differential lock for superior corner-exit traction. The chassis has been meticulously preserved, with documented rear subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension geometry utilizing OEM bushings to maintain its razor-sharp handling characteristics. This is a turn-key collector piece with zero deferred maintenance, offering the peak analog driving experience.",
