      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector-grade specimen, meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment and showing absolutely zero signs of wear. The factory paint retains its original deep luster with no swirls, scratches, or stone chips, while the interior remains in showroom state with pristine leather surfaces and a flawless dashboard. Every electronic feature functions perfectly, from the premium sound system to the advanced driver assists. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, with a comprehensive service history documented exclusively through certified master technicians. It comes complete with both original keys, all factory manuals, and a tailored car cover. This is an uncompromising choice for the buyer who demands a vehicle indistinguishable from new.",
