      "description": "Offering a pristine E46 M3, a masterclass in high-revving, naturally aspirated performance. This specimen features the iconic S54B32 straight-six engine, complete with individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been fully bulletproofed for timing precision. The chassis integrity is superlative, featuring proactive subframe reinforcement and a factory-spec Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox that offers crisp, mechanical gate selection. Power is delivered through a variable M differential lock, ensuring maximum traction across the rear axle. Suspension kinematics are tight, utilizing original McPherson struts and a multi-link rear setup with zero bushing deflection. This is an investment-grade vehicle with a flawless service history, tailored for the purist who demands mechanical perfection and linear throttle response.",
